{"data":[{"date":"09:09 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Pakistan vs U23 Nepal 16h ng\u00e0y 19/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/nhan-dinh-u23-pakistan-vs-u23-nepal-16h-ngay-198-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Pakistan vs U23 Nepal l\u00fac 16h ng\u00e0y 19/8(V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Pakistan vs U23 Nepal 16h ng\u00e0y 198 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Pakistan vs U23 Nepal 16h ng\u00e0y 198 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/u23-pakistan-vs-u23-nepal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Pakistan vs U23 Nepal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span>U23 Pakistan vs U23 Nepal: 2-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nC\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm ng\u00e3 ng\u0169 t\u1eeb l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi 2 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i U23 Pakistan vs U23 Nepal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u1edbt d\u00e0nh cho 4/6 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i n\u00e0y may ra m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eadm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5 t\u1ed1t khi \u0111em ra c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 kh\u00e1c. N\u1ebfu hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f2a nhau th\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn 100% s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i. U23 Nepal ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a U23 Pakistan l\u1ea1i \u0103n \u00fd h\u01a1n. V\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea3 hai s\u1ebd d\u1ed1c t\u1ed5ng l\u1ef1c ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean gia d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 U23 Pakistan l\u1eabn U23 Nepal c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018. N\u00ean c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf tin r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1edfi m\u1edf c\u00f9ng NHI\u1ec0U B\u00c0N TH\u1eaeNG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2535","checkdouble":"194791"},{"date":"09:29 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 UAE vs U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c 19h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/nhan-dinh-u23-uae-vs-u23-trung-quoc-19h00-ngay-198-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 UAE vs U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 UAE vs U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c 19h00 ng\u00e0y 198 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 UAE vs U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c 19h00 ng\u00e0y 198 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/U23-Trung-quoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 UAE vs U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span>U23 UAE vs U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c: 1-2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nU23 UAE m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 b\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Syria v\u00e0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng U23 Timor Lester 4-1, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 U23 Syria. Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i n\u00e0y, U23 UAE ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp trong khi U23 Syria ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p U23 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu v\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi tay h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, U23 UAE n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 th\u1eb3ng (d\u00e0nh cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u) th\u00ec b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p U23 Syria \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 \u0110\u00f4ng\u00a0Timor th\u00ec l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng - b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng. Th\u1ef1c ra, n\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra th\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 b\u1edfi v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tay th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m 4 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf 6 b\u1ea3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 U23 UAE c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1edfi U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1eb1ng 2 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ghi 9 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ph\u1ec9a v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng. U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00ean h\u1ecd m\u00e0 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c, U23 UAE kh\u00f3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xep hang tai bang C sau 2 luot tran\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/bang-C.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2534","checkdouble":"194792"},{"date":"09:49 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor vs U23 Syria 19h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/nhan-dinh-u23-dong-timor-vs-u23-syria-19h00-ngay-198-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Old Trafford chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng ra \u0111i khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng sau ba n\u0103m, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man Utd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1edf ph\u00e0o nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5p th\u1ecfm \u00e2u lo v\u1ec1 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t \u0111i David De Gea, tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c Chelsea ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00ec Kepa Arrizabalanga. N\u00f3i chung, c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 y\u00ean v\u1ecb v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, th\u1ebf n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c De Gea ra \u0111i trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/mourinho-khang-dinh-de-gea-co-gia-0-dong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Man Utd d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c anh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tin vui \u0111\u1ebfn cho to\u00e0n Old Trafford theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1 h\u00f3m h\u1ec9nh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 0 \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i y\u00eau qu\u00fd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 th\u1eadt may m\u1eafn khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng suy ngh\u0129 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00f4i khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta qu\u00ean th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Gi\u1edd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 Alisson v\u00e0 Kepa, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a David r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1edbt gi\u00e1 th\u00ea th\u1ea3m tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho ai h\u1ebft, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 CLB, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3, c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho MU. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec ph\u1ea7n vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u1ea3 ba b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thu-mon-thong-tri-mua-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-bon-thap-nien-binh-thuong-hoa-mot-tu-tuong-di-biet-172-194190.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/klopp-phan-khoi-khi-kepa-pha-ky-luc-cua-alisson.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thu-mon-thong-tri-mua-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-bon-thap-nien-binh-thuong-hoa-mot-tu-tuong-di-biet-172-194190.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng: B\u1ed1n th\u1eadp ni\u00ean b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f3a m\u1ed9t t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng d\u1ecb bi\u1ec7t</span><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. Ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n Alisson v\u00e0 Kepa c\u0169ng l\u00e0 hai b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2533","checkdouble":"194793"},{"date":"10:15 19/08","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/goc-nhin-olympic-viet-nam-da-hay-buong-tran-gap-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Khi m\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c hay bu\u00f4ng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i?\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<h2>B\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh thay \u0111\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D, b\u1edfi l\u00fac n\u00e0y hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang b\u1eb1ng nhau \u1edf m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean BXH. C\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n n\u00e0o, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, n\u1ebfu hai \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00f2a nhau trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00ec theo lu\u1eadt, c\u1ea3 hai s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00fac n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua Malaysia. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p x\u1ebfp nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Malaysia, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Goc-nhin-Olympic-Viet-Nam-da-hay-buong-tran-gap-Nhat-Ban-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng D ASIAD tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1ea5t hay nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi quan tr\u1ecdng?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, n\u1ebfu Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, theo c\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n chia c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B (c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan, Qatar), ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng E (Bahrain, Kyrgyzstan, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c) ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea3ng F (Iran, Saudi Arabia hay Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c g\u1eb7p to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Malaysia v\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u1eeda th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n, d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Olympic Malaysia kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng khi v\u1eeba c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i trong khu v\u1ef1c \u0110N\u00c1, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o e ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Malaysia. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Ong Kim Swee t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1edd toan t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch tr\u00ean, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea5t gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8, m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u00edt c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u thay cho V\u0103n Thanh b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Khi \u0111\u00f3 V\u0103n Thanh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Goc-nhin-Olympic-Viet-Nam-da-hay-buong-tran-gap-Nhat-Ban-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd c\u00f9ng H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng. Song c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng hay \u0110\u1ee9c Huy. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n khi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 cho Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i. Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u00f2ng trong.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n h\u1ebft vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea5t \u0111i nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u r\u1ee7i ro c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Khi m\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Thanh hay Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng,\u2026 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n th\u00ec s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Park Hang Seo\" title=\"Park Hang Seo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103n HLV\u00a0Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd tung \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00ecnh L\u1ee3i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n. C\u1ea3 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 th\u1eeba khao kh\u00e1t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn, v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia-168-194784.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia-168-194784.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8): Khi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 19/8, c\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn tranh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-mai-duc-chung-dt-viet-nam-se-danh-bai-thai-lan-168-194746.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/hlv-mai-duc-chung-dt-viet-nam-se-danh-bai-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-mai-duc-chung-dt-viet-nam-se-danh-bai-thai-lan-168-194746.html\">HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung: \u201c\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan\u201d</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 18 di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 18h30 ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi, HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194745.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194745.html\">B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD</span><br>\r\nT\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Th\u00e1i Lan, SiamSport m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t ASIAD 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-soc-malaysia-han-quoc-van-co-kha-nang-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194711.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/11/thua-soc-malaysia-han-quoc-van-co-kha-nang-gap-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-soc-malaysia-han-quoc-van-co-kha-nang-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194711.html\">Thua s\u1ed1c Malaysia, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTheo c\u00e1ch chia b\u1ea3ng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2532","checkdouble":"194794"},{"date":"11:01 19/08","title":"Sarri gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u00ec sao Chelsea b\u1ecb l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/sarri-giai-thich-vi-sao-chelsea-bi-loi-nguoc-dong-trong-hiep-mot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd qua \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Arsenal v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ba \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 th\u1ea3nh th\u01a1i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Marcos Alonso t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u \u1edf th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/sarri-giai-thich-vi-sao-chelsea-bi-loi-nguoc-dong-trong-hiep-mot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn hai b\u00e0n ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh tan th\u00e0nh m\u00e2y kh\u00f3i ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng b\u1ed1n ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Iwobi tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 ng\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Maurizio Sarri vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd sau tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf: \u201cTh\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u1edbi ba \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00fang v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00ean b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngay t\u1eeb trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 15 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u00f3.\"<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1ef1 ly \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb k\u00e9o gi\u00e3n ra qu\u00e1 xa v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nhau. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 15 ph\u00fat m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u01a1i pressing \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7, ch\u00ednh th\u1ebf m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn 4-5 l\u1ea7n s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 chao \u0111\u1ea3o t\u1eeb Arsenal.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Arsenal v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Premier League 2018/19 sau hai tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u00e1u \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i. V\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Sarri s\u1ebd h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn St. James\u2019 Park l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng Newcastle.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Video tr\u1eadn Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</h2>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2531","checkdouble":"194795"},{"date":"11:25 19/08","title":"Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh De Gea c\u00f3 gi\u00e1... 0 \u0111\u1ed3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/mourinho-khang-dinh-de-gea-co-gia-0-dong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Old Trafford chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng ra \u0111i khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng sau ba n\u0103m, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man Utd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1edf ph\u00e0o nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5p th\u1ecfm \u00e2u lo v\u1ec1 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t \u0111i David De Gea, tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c Chelsea ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00ec Kepa Arrizabalanga. N\u00f3i chung, c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 y\u00ean v\u1ecb v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, th\u1ebf n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c De Gea ra \u0111i trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/mourinho-khang-dinh-de-gea-co-gia-0-dong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Man Utd d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c anh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tin vui \u0111\u1ebfn cho to\u00e0n Old Trafford theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1 h\u00f3m h\u1ec9nh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 0 \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i y\u00eau qu\u00fd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 th\u1eadt may m\u1eafn khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng suy ngh\u0129 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00f4i khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta qu\u00ean th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Gi\u1edd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 Alisson v\u00e0 Kepa, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a David r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1edbt gi\u00e1 th\u00ea th\u1ea3m tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho ai h\u1ebft, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 CLB, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3, c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho MU. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec ph\u1ea7n vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u1ea3 ba b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thu-mon-thong-tri-mua-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-bon-thap-nien-binh-thuong-hoa-mot-tu-tuong-di-biet-172-194190.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/klopp-phan-khoi-khi-kepa-pha-ky-luc-cua-alisson.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thu-mon-thong-tri-mua-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-bon-thap-nien-binh-thuong-hoa-mot-tu-tuong-di-biet-172-194190.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng: B\u1ed1n th\u1eadp ni\u00ean b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f3a m\u1ed9t t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng d\u1ecb bi\u1ec7t</span><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. Ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n Alisson v\u00e0 Kepa c\u0169ng l\u00e0 hai b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2530","checkdouble":"194796"},{"date":"11:51 19/08","title":"Arsenal thua \u0111au, Emery v\u1eabn vui v\u00ec Ozil... bi\u1ebft nghe l\u1eddi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/arsenal-thua-dau-emery-van-vui-vi-ozil-biet-nghe-loi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n HLV x\u1ee9 Basque h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn derby London g\u1eb7p Chelsea.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng san b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t hai b\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm t\u1ea1o ra, Arsenal cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i tr\u1eafng tay ra v\u1ec1 khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcos Alonso l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac trong th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng \u1edf derby London n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-chelsea-vs-arsenal-32-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194768.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u Ozil tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u Ozil tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/arsenal-thua-dau-emery-van-vui-vi-ozil-biet-nghe-loi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u Ozil tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Emery c\u00f3 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Ozil v\u1ec1 \u00fd th\u1ee9c tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u1ea7u ti\u1ebfn. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cH\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i vui v\u00ec nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra s\u00e2n ch\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u00eam s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u00f3 \u0111ang b\u1ecb Chelsea chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea9y ng\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda sau.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp hai tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea, Arsenal \u0111ang ti\u1ec7m c\u1eadn nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf Premier League nh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu h\u01a1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n sau s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn derby London kh\u00e1c khi Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Ham.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian-172-194779.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian-172-194779.html\">Arsenal thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp: Unai Emery c\u1ea7n th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau th\u1eddi gian?</span><br>\r\nTh\u00eam nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed5 x\u1ebb sau khi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 thua Chelsea nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Unai Emery v\u1eabn mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2529","checkdouble":"194797"},{"date":"11:21 19/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/8: B\u01a1i l\u1ed9i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft hai n\u1ed9i dung","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-198.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/8: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, th\u00f4ng tin, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c V\u0110V thu\u1ed9c \u0111o\u00e0n th\u1ec3 thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- 11h10: B\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec1n: \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n b\u1ea3ng B, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0nh cho n\u1eef, tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 (11-25, 15-25 v\u00e0 13-25) tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean cho t\u1ea5m HCV, Trung Qu\u1ed1c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n- 11h00: T\u1ea1i m\u00f4n Wushu, n\u1eef V\u0110V&nbsp;Tr\u1ea7n Th\u1ecb Kh\u00e1nh Ly \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 b\u00e0i Th\u00e1i c\u1ef1c quy\u1ec1n n\u1eef v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m 9,68 trong khi V\u0110V&nbsp;Trung&nbsp;Qu\u1ed1c d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m 9,75. Ng\u00e0y mai, c\u00f4 s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed1t b\u00e0i Th\u00e1i c\u1ef1c ki\u1ebfm n\u1eef.&nbsp;T\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m hai b\u00e0i n\u00e0y m\u1edbi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e9t huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u1ed9t n\u1ed9i dung bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1c (Nam quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 Nam \u0110ao), n\u1eef V\u0110V&nbsp;Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00f9y Linh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1t 9,45 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf b\u00e0i Nam quy\u1ec1n, x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 6/12 V\u0110V tham d\u1ef1 k\u00e9m xa V\u0110V&nbsp;d\u1eabn d\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Trung Qu\u1ed1c, qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f4n Wushu (9,75 \u0111i\u1ec3m). <br>\r\n<br>\r\n- 10h35: B\u1eafn s\u00fang: T\u1ea1i N\u1ed9i dung 10m s\u00fang tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u01a1i h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p nam/n\u1eef, Nguy\u1ec5n Duy Ho\u00e0ng v\u00e0 Awaki Ai ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m 806,4 v\u00e0 x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed 20/22 \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 n\u1ed9i dung n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- 10h20: \u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i quy\u1ec1n n\u1eef Taekwondo Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8: Sau khi th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ed9i Trung Qu\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1eef taekwondo Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo. D\u00f9 k\u00e9m \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf b\u00e0i thi 1 v\u1edbi 8.020 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi 8.040 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i Trung Qu\u1ed1c, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i taekwondo Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf b\u00e0i thi th\u1ee9 hai, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRi\u00eang &quot;n\u1eef ho\u00e0ng Taekwondo&quot; Ch\u00e2u Tuy\u1ebft V\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft n\u1ed9i dung quy\u1ec1n bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u1eef: C\u00f4 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia Rosmaniar Defia \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft n\u1ed9i dung n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Ch\u00e2u Tuy\u1ebft V\u00e2n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 8.330, thua v\u00f5 s\u0129 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia, Defia Rosmaniar \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 8.460.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- 10h00: V\u0110V&nbsp;Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u, L\u00ea Nguy\u1ec5n Paul v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft 100 m ng\u1eeda nam: \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u01a1i th\u1ee9 hai v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i, anh c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 55 gi\u00e2y 47. Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 8 v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i (x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 6), qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o b\u01a1i chung k\u1ebft.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/anh9_2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- 09h35: Ho\u00e0ng Qu\u00fd Ph\u01b0\u1edbc thi v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i 200 m t\u1ef1 do: K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, anh \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 1 ph\u00fat 49 gi\u00e2y 68, \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 8 v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t thi chung k\u1ebft tranh ch\u1ea5p huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, V\u0110V c\u1ee7a Trung Qu\u1ed1c Sun Yang c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i n\u1ed9i dung n\u00e0y 1 ph\u00fat 47 gi\u00e2y 58.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/anh8_2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- 09h15: Mai Th\u1ecb Linh thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i n\u1ed9i dung 1.500m t\u1ef1 do n\u1eef v\u00e0 c\u00f4 x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t thi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m 3 V\u0110V v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 17 ph\u00fat 40 gi\u00e2y 56, k\u00e9m ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u h\u01a1n 32 gi\u00e2y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 21 b\u1ed9 huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao \u1edf c\u00e1c m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u1ebfm (2), b\u1eafn s\u00fang (2), b\u01a1i l\u1ed9i (7), taekwondo (4), \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eadt (5) v\u00e0 wushu (1). Ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta n\u1eb1m \u1edf m\u00f4n Taekwondo khi di\u1ec5n ra n\u1ed9i dung quy\u1ec1n bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n nam/n\u1eef.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp gi\u1eefa tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan,\u1edf m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef, di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 18h30.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 198 B\u01a1i l\u1ed9i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft hai n\u1ed9i dung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 198 B\u01a1i l\u1ed9i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft hai n\u1ed9i dung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Truc-tiep-Asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-198,-ket-qua-Asiad-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 198 B\u01a1i l\u1ed9i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft hai n\u1ed9i dung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 198 B\u01a1i l\u1ed9i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft hai n\u1ed9i dung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/TRUC-TIEP-ASIAD-2018-ngay-hom-nay-198-Boi-loi-Viet-Nam-vao-chung-ket-hai-noi-dung-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 198 B\u01a1i l\u1ed9i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft hai n\u1ed9i dung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 198 B\u01a1i l\u1ed9i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft hai n\u1ed9i dung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/lich-thi-dau-asiad-2-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y 19/8 c\u1ee7a TTVN</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2528","checkdouble":"194798"},{"date":"11:33 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Uzbekistan 19h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/nhan-dinh-u23-thai-lan-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h00-ngay-198-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Uzbekistan l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Uzbekistan 19h00 ng\u00e0y 198 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Uzbekistan 19h00 ng\u00e0y 198 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/U23_Uzbekistan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Uzbekistan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span>U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Uzbekistan: 1-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nU23 Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1eebng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft ASIAD 2014 n\u00ean t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 th\u1ea5p \u1edf Asiad 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u00e0o ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd, U23 Th\u00e1i\u00a0Lan l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 v\u00e0 \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn chia tay ASIAD ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u00f2a 2 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi U23 Qatar v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t U23 Bangladesh v\u1ed1n thua xa v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tay, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng m\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp b\u1edfi \u1edf c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i (U23 Qatar vs U23 Bangladesh) c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p U23 Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng Uzbekistan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, U23 Uzbekistan - \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m Asiad 2018 - \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ea v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. H\u1ecd chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Bangladesh, ti\u1ebfp sau l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u00f2n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng h\u01a1n g\u1ea5p b\u1ed9i khi \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p U23 Qatar \u0111\u1ebfn 6-0. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady h\u1ecd s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1edf h\u1eefu lu\u00f4n ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc h\u1ecd s\u1ebd bu\u00f4ng xu\u00f4i. Gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng U23 Uzbekistan th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xep hang tai bang B sau 2 luot tran\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/bang-B.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2527","checkdouble":"194799"},{"date":"11:47 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Qatar 19h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/nhan-dinh-u23-bangladesh-vs-u23-qatar-19h00-ngay-198-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Qatar l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Qatar 19h00 ng\u00e0y 198 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Qatar 19h00 ng\u00e0y 198 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/U23_Qatar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Qatar</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span>U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Qatar: 1-3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u0110\u1ec3 thua U23 Uzbekistan \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018, \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 U23 Bangladesh \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ee7 h\u00f2a U23 Th\u00e1i Lan, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn tuy nhi\u00ean 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi qu\u1ed1c gia Nam \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u1ee7a U23 Bangladesh \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 Qatar v\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng U23 Uzbekistan th\u00ec h\u1ecd s\u1ebd x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 chung cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Qatar c\u0169ng trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 khi \u0111ang c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tay (h\u00f2a U23 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i t\u1edbi 0-6 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uzbekistan). M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i\u00a0U23 Uzbekistan (\u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1edf h\u1eefu lu\u00f4n ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00ean tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n mang t\u00ednh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c) th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1eabn s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch 1/4 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t b\u1edfi c\u00f3 trong tay 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0y, U23 Qatar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi U23 Bangladesh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o U23 Qatar nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 Bangladesh 3-0 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xep hang tai bang B sau 2 luot tran\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/bang-B.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2526","checkdouble":"194800"},{"date":"07:10 19/08","title":"Lionel Messi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Philippe Coutinho - nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \"ba sao\" c\u1ee7a Barcelona tr\u01b0\u1edbc Alaves.</h2><h2>B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Messi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Alaves l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Lionel Messi ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh &quot;Leo&quot; l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn hai pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn khung g\u1ed7 gi\u00fap Barca gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde nhan xet bat ngo ve Lionel Messi sau tran thang Alaves.\" title=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Alaves.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/hlv-ernesto-valverde-nhan-xet-bat-ngo-ve-lionel-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Alaves.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Ernesto Valverde th\u1ed1t l\u00ean: &quot;Messi lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Anh \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ng\u1eebng kinh ng\u1ea1c. Th\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea5y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6.000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Barca chia s\u1ebb ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Levante khi b\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Valverde gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Valverde ch\u01b0a s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t khi c\u00f2n c\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf ngo\u00e0i nh\u01b0 Coutinho. Nh\u00f3m t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, Arthur v\u00e0 Vidal ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV Valverde cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng hi\u1ec7p hai l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Coutinho v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i b\u00f3ng, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3. S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00ean m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng&quot;.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Barca m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/lich-thi-dau/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga-181-194781.html\">Lionel Messi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-barca-vs-alaves-30-highlights-la-liga-2018-328-194780.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Barca 3-0 Alaves (V\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/barca-vs-alaves-la-liga-1882018-372-194762.html\">Barca 3-0 Alaves: Messi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Blaugrana ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0 \u00fd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-tai-tieng-cua-barca-hanh-phuc-sau-man-chao-san-camp-nou-180-194707.html\">T\u00e2n binh tai ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Barca h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Camp Nou</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/anh-trai-messi-di-tu-vi-toi-tang-tru-vu-khi-188-194681.html\">Anh trai Messi \u0111i t\u00f9 v\u00ec t\u1ed9i t\u00e0ng tr\u1eef v\u0169 kh\u00ed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lionel-messi-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-barca-mua-toi-180-194656.html\">Lionel Messi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2525","checkdouble":"194781"},{"date":"07:17 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield (19h30 ng\u00e0y 19/8): \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-man-city-vs-huddersfield-19h30-ngay-198-don-gian-la-chua-the-can.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u00eam ba \u0111i\u1ec3m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c n\u1eefa ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau duy nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n trong t\u1ea7m tay c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u00ec m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Etihad ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng Premier League, Manchester City kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi v\u1eabn nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng tr\u1ea3i qua ba th\u00e1ng ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 n\u00e0o h\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-man-city-vs-huddersfield-19h30-ngay-198-don-gian-la-chua-the-can.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, hai b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u01a1i x\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i d\u1ea1ng v\u1eeba ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal. Ch\u1eb3ng quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u1edf Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh r\u1ed3i ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Man City c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 n\u00e9t \u1edf vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t hay s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Etihad \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng Nicolas Otamendi, David Silva hay c\u1ea3 Kevin De Bruyne, n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u1eabn b\u0103ng b\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-02-man-city-sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-anh-172-194405.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/du-am-arsenal-02-man-city-sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-02-man-city-sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-anh-172-194405.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal 0-2 Man City: Sterling v\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Raheem Sterling m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Man City trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn ba th\u00e1ng xem ra kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eb7n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Man City, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u00eanh thang v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu, cho \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng M\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i mang t\u00ean Liverpool.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng De Bruyne, Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i qu\u1ef5 ng\u00e3, th\u1ebf n\u00ean nh\u1eefng Huddersfield hay Wolverhampton, Newcastle, Fulham, Cardiff, Brighton s\u1eafp t\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec khi ngh\u00eanh chi\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 vua, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Bernardo Silva nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp thay th\u1ebf De Bruyne, hay t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c Riyad Mahrez, c\u1ea3 Benjamin Mendy v\u00e0 Aymeric Laporte c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling tran Arsenal vs Man City\" title=\"Sterling tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Du-am-Arsenal-0-2-Man-City-Sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-Anh-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Etihad c\u1ee7a Huddersfield Town c\u00f3 ch\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u00e0ng \u00edt b\u00e0n thua c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u0169ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh gi\u1eadm ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i th\u1ee5t l\u00f9i, trong khi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng d\u1ea7n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3, Huddersfield ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn bu\u00f4ng xu\u00f4i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t ba b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu t\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 David Wagner.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thong-diep-tu-huddersfield-hay-cu-tin-di-va-dung-bao-gio-ngung-172-185994.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/10/DcyGxr0W4AA33Sj.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thong-diep-tu-huddersfield-hay-cu-tin-di-va-dung-bao-gio-ngung-172-185994.html\">Th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p t\u1eeb Huddersfield: H\u00e3y c\u1ee9 tin \u0111i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eebng bao ng\u1edd ng\u1eebng!</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Chelsea ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch Stamford Bridge, Huddersfield tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng Premier League th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1eddi th\u1ef1c cho ri\u00eang...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ef1a trung l\u1ea1i, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 Man City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 t\u1ed1i nay, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t bao nhi\u00eau m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng c\u0169ng v\u1edbi chuy\u1ebfn vi\u1ebfng th\u0103m Etihad g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, ch\u00ednh Huddersfield \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ng\u00e0y vui s\u1edbm \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1eady n\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola r\u00fat ra kinh nghi\u1ec7m. N\u1ebfu ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Huddersfield kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i v\u1eadt \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 vua ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Nhan-dinh-Man-City-vs-Huddersfield-19h30-ngay-198-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man City (4-3-3): 31. Ederson; 2. Walker \u2013 5. Stones \u2013 14. Laporte \u2013 22. Mendy; 8. Gundogan \u2013 25. Fernandinho \u2013 20. Bernardo; 26. Mahrez \u2013 33. Jesus \u2013 7. Sterling<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Huddersfield (4-2-3-1): 12. Hamer; 33. Hadergjonaj \u2013 26. Schindler \u2013 5. Kongolo \u2013 15. Lowe; 10. Mooy \u2013 6. Hogg; 17. Van La Parra \u2013 21. Pritchard \u2013 11. Diakhaby; 24. Mounie<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield: 4-0<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p><strong><br>\r\n</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2524","checkdouble":"194783"},{"date":"07:25 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8): Khi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 19/8, c\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn tranh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hay gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7?\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; khi gi\u1eef l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 sau hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u khi c\u00f3 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/ b\u1ea1i l\u00e0 +5 (b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt song t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u BXH b\u1ea3ng D do h\u01a1n hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 fair-play. N\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00f2a nhau th\u00ec sau 90 ph\u00fat, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 198) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 198) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Nhan-dinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nhat-Ban-(16h00-ngay-198)-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ea7y Park c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u1ee7a 1 trong 3 b\u1ea3ng B/E/F, trong khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D g\u1eb7p nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, d\u00f9 th\u1eafng, h\u00f2a hay b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i th\u00ec \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo 99% kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e1p m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kim chi \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0nh cho 16 \u0111\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u1ed1 c\u1ea3nh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng nh\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Uzbekistan, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh 1 su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft th\u00ec nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1nh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng &ldquo;bu\u00f4ng&rdquo; tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 m\u1ed1i lo ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n, kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u1edf cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn chi\u1ec1u nay nh\u1eb1m c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bang D ASIAD\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng D ASIAD\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Bang-D-ASIAD.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D l\u00fac n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm vinh quang t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 v\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n &ndash; khi danh hi\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb U21 tham d\u1ef1 nh\u1eb1m c\u1ecd s\u00e1t v\u00e0 trau d\u1ed3i kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Olympic Tokyo 2020, k\u1ef3 th\u1ebf v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng b\u1edfi l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng toan t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan, Nepal \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Vi\u1ec7t Nam. D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, nh\u1edd s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Pakistan vs U23 Nhat Ban\" title=\"U23 Pakistan vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/u23-nhat-ban-vs-u23-pakistan-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m t\u1eebng \u0111\u0103ng quang gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia l\u00e0 Thebault Yamaguchi v\u00e0 Tatsuya Ito. V\u00e0 d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i U21, song ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Uzbekistan, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i U21 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 c\u00f3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. T\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1eeb c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb cho \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110TQG. Tr\u1ea3i qua 4 l\u1ea7n so t\u00e0i cao th\u1ea5p, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf to\u00e0n thua, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng mang t\u00ednh danh d\u1ef1.&nbsp;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u1edbi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i b\u00e0n tay c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sau l\u00fac n\u00e0y 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 n\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh cho v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u nay. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng; Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i, V\u0103n Thanh; \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Ryosuke Kojima; Takahiro Yanagi; Teruki Hara; Honoya Shoji; Taiyo Koga; So Fujitani; Itsuki Urata; Koji Miyoshi; Tsukasa Morishima; Kyosuke Tagawa; Ren Komatsu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: 0-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2523","checkdouble":"194784"},{"date":"07:48 19/08","title":"HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/hlv-ernesto-valverde-nhan-xet-bat-ngo-ve-lionel-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Philippe Coutinho - nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \"ba sao\" c\u1ee7a Barcelona tr\u01b0\u1edbc Alaves.</h2><h2>B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Messi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Alaves l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Lionel Messi ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh &quot;Leo&quot; l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn hai pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn khung g\u1ed7 gi\u00fap Barca gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde nhan xet bat ngo ve Lionel Messi sau tran thang Alaves.\" title=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Alaves.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/hlv-ernesto-valverde-nhan-xet-bat-ngo-ve-lionel-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Alaves.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Ernesto Valverde th\u1ed1t l\u00ean: &quot;Messi lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Anh \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ng\u1eebng kinh ng\u1ea1c. Th\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea5y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6.000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Barca chia s\u1ebb ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Levante khi b\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Valverde gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Valverde ch\u01b0a s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t khi c\u00f2n c\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf ngo\u00e0i nh\u01b0 Coutinho. Nh\u00f3m t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, Arthur v\u00e0 Vidal ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV Valverde cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng hi\u1ec7p hai l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Coutinho v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i b\u00f3ng, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3. S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00ean m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng&quot;.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Barca m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/lich-thi-dau/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga-181-194781.html\">Lionel Messi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-barca-vs-alaves-30-highlights-la-liga-2018-328-194780.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Barca 3-0 Alaves (V\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/barca-vs-alaves-la-liga-1882018-372-194762.html\">Barca 3-0 Alaves: Messi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Blaugrana ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0 \u00fd</spa